title: Astounding - missing five issues
description:
This torrent contains all but the March 1945, April 1945, Dec 1956, June 1958 and Dec 1958 issues of Astounding. Those will be torrented when they become available.

Restored covers and UK editions are included in the torrent.

This torrent is itself a torrent file. Download it and use it as usual. Pirate Bay has a 200 kb limit on the size of torrent files, and this one is larger.
